title: Vice President Mike Pence to Visit Nashville, TN – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			
Issued on:
October 2, 2019
On Monday, October 7th, Vice President Mike Pence will travel to Nashville, TN.  There, the Vice President will deliver remarks at Tyson Foods, highlighting the benefits of the United States-Mexico-Canada Agreement and how it will create a level playing field for American companies to compete and win on the world stage.Additional details about the Vice President’s trip are forthcoming.
